{"tid":2412131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彩雲邨麥當勞有顧客疑拒用電子腳鐐襲擊職員","createTime":"2021-02-18T00:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T00:49:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35347a2c1637d39bd238a6423ea01943b814127c","tid":2412131,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:14:55.000Z","msg":"彩雲邨麥當勞有顧客疑拒用安心出行襲擊職員 <br />\n<br />\n牛池灣彩雲邨商場麥當勞餐廳發生襲擊案，一名職員受傷。事發在清晨近7點，職員報案指，一名男顧客拒絕使用政府「安心出行」二維碼程式，與職員爭執，期間有人用手機襲擊職員。 <br />\n<br />\n本港今日起放寬社交距離措施，當中食肆堂食延長至晚上10時，每枱最多4人，負責人須確保顧客，利用手機掃描「安心出行」場所二維碼，或登記有關人士的姓名、聯絡電話及到訪處所的日期及時間。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2379451&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOtqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=c0ced2f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379451</a>"},{"pid":"b80f25f29bab41ef89fdbe4fa6538e1de6d909db","tid":2412131,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"港共嘅on9政策逼人做，打9個店員做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共產黨最鐘意就係人民鬥人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b41783a3460fb2e860f444e128aa10736c6cc20","tid":2412131,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:48:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">第一滴血出現</span>"},{"pid":"a6371267815245b7854c545c40c12c617ce9a40d","tid":2412131,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:49:13.000Z","msg":"職員又性幻想間鋪佢有份啦"},{"pid":"be9c8ec94bd47d869ec3e08f1f0b6fea813893fc","tid":2412131,"uid":149925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:49:33.000Z","msg":"第一單花生"}]}